A variant of [[iw|īw]], cognate with Old Saxon [[ich|īch]], Old High German [[igo|īgo]].

====Pronunciation====
[[IPA]]: /e:oh/

====Noun====
'''ēoh'''
# a [[yew]] tree
# the runic character ᛇ (/eo/ or /e:o/)

